data.description:
1. Binance: All services are gradually being restored, and the withdrawal function has been reopened;
2. Galaxy Digital's associated wallet has withdrawn 9,368 ETH from Binance and Bullish.com;
3. Matrixport: Stablecoin funds continue to flow in, showing the resilience and application growth of the crypto market;
4. Binance will remove the VIDT/BTC spot trading pair;
5. Ethereum Foundation members: ERC-7786 will enhance cross-chain messaging, and related discussions will be held on April 16;
6. US Vice President Vance: The United States and the United Kingdom are likely to reach a "great deal" on trade;
7. Bank of America survey: Global investors are selling US stocks at a record rate;
8. The probability of the Federal Reserve cutting interest rates by 25 basis points in May has dropped to 16%;
9. Bank of America survey: 82% of respondents believe that the global economy will weaken, reaching a 30-year high;
10. Market analysis: US Treasury bonds seem to have temporarily stabilized;
11. Google will implement the new MiCA crypto advertising regulations in Europe from April 23;
12. Bitcoin's 14-year return rate is 72,000 times, far exceeding the S&P 500's 306% and gold's 116%.
